Sure, here are some example sentences in Serbian that use the word "hodam" in different forms and positions:

1. Ja *hodam* svaki dan po parku. (I *walk* every day in the park.)
2. Ti *hodaš* veoma brzo. (You *walk* very fast.)
3. On *hoda* uz pomoć štaka. (He *walks* with the help of crutches.)
4. Mi *hodamo* do prodavnice. (We *walk* to the store.)
5. Vi *hodate* po kiši bez kišobrana? (Are you *walking* in the rain without an umbrella?)
6. Oni *hodaju* uz obalu reke. (They *walk* along the riverbank.)

Note: The word "hodam" is highlighted with an asterisk (*) in each sentence. The translations of each sentence in English are provided in parentheses.